Mere paas teri video hai promise ki ki tu milne aaega pakke se.  Jaob kahin bhi lagi, saal ki ek trip pakki. Ye faaltu vaala promise nai hai, I really mean it.  Mai kitni baar hall2 vaale room aati thi par tu kaafi comfortable tha usse (swapnil to gaand fati mein hi rehta tha poore timeðŸ˜…). Bohot maze kiye apan ne us room mein, kitni acchi memories. Tere kuuch embarrassing videos bhi hai mere paas(hints are: lip gloss and yellow). Nai milne aaya to leak kar dungi.  Bohot sad thi mai jab tu jaa raha tha Kanpur se last month. Honestly maine and Anany ne bhi tab hi jaane ka plan bana liya tha.  RM mein sasti daaru ka alag hi feel hai, kya pata baad mein utna maza ho na ho. 
Tu hamesha Gupta kaaju hi rahega ðŸ’™

author: Gunjan  Jalori

text:
CRINGE ALERT!!
It started with scaring other couples on the skywalk and ended with, NO, it never ended :). You can never imagine how much you meant to me at the time we met. You still have no idea how precious those late-night walks were, how beautiful the sun looked at 5 am with you, how you just understood what I meant, how you just knew what to say at every fucking time, how you always kept my priorities at top, how you never really complained about anything, how you made me laugh even if it wasnâ€™t necessary. I know everything you did required patience and dedication, I know it wasnâ€™t easy for you to get out of your comfort zone but there wasnâ€™t even one single time when you backed out. You are the most rational boyfriend one could expect. Even when we were fighting, you were there for me. Many of the things can not be written here but I know you'll always feel them while reading this. I do and always will appreciate those little things, our walks on "footpaths" both inside and outside campus, our first date in bazooka, sneaking through moti jheel barricades, the gatecrash in Kanpur, binging tv series, our spot(wink) and infinite other things. I know I can get too competitive and sometimes it can be difficult but you never uttered a word. I am extremely happy for us to have crossed many challenges that came in our relationship. It was as close to ideal as WE could get. We had our quirks and weirdness. I like having really conversations with you, I love sharing the "we could go to jail for this" humor with you. I love that you typed my pet name exactly 69 times in my memoir. I love a million things about you and I can fill pages but can not. You'll know them. I just want to say one thing, there may be a thousand ways in which a relationship MAY or may NOT go, but I know we'll choose what will work best for us. LOVE YOU MOTU ðŸ–¤

PS:  Even if we decide to break up, I REALLY hope our friendship stays this magical. :)

text:
Hii Jay. R. 

I will always spell your name wrong. I will always end it with an R and always call you each of those "not at all offensive" words :). Kitna bhi rr karle tu, I will always tease you for what you "have" and "do not have." Because I have full Faith in our friendship (ðŸ˜‰).

When we first met, I didn't know what was going on under the hood, and I guess neither did you. You started a streak for my birthdays. Jab mujhe Mudreka ne bola ki poem likh raha hai tu, I thought vo mock kar raha hai meko.  I hope that trend never ends. I always loved your gifts, kaafi efforts bhare hote the unme. I felt a different beautiful connection with you. Gh ke saamne vaali net ke paas jo hum baithe the, vo night hi best lagti hai mujhe aaj tak, that was the first time you kinda opened up. 

Uske baad to walks exponentially hi badh gayi, kaafi campus naap liya humne. I learned a lot un walks pe and I know you did too. Kitna fattu hai tu yaar. Green vaali night mein tune hi concepts batae the and teri hi fat gayiðŸ˜‚.  Kaafi saari baate aisi hai jo likhi nai jaa sakti and shayad likh ke unki importance kam ho jaegi par you still have a special place in my life which will remain reserved for you

Even though our interactions got limited. I am glad to still have that near-perfect connection every time we talk. I know agar apan 10 saal ke baad bhi baat karenge to bhi I can make infi fun of you. Vaise tujhe apni deal yaad hai na? Bhulna mat vo. :)

Lots of loveðŸ–¤
PS: I still think Bezaubernd doesn't suit me xD

Hii Aunty,
Vaise to mai nai likh paati zyada par I can write books for you. Memoir likhna fir bhi tough hai kyuki bohot bhasad hai likhne ko dimag mein jise usually tu hi organize karti thi. My advice to all: Agar Medha ko sirf 25 percent bhi follow kar liya na to poori college life optimize ho jaegi. Kaafi chaapu hai tu aise hi rehna.

Ab sun, kyuki life mein sirf ek hi baar bolungi, you are the sweetest, kindest and PUREST person on this whole fucking planet. Pehli baar drying area ki bench pe mile the and ghanto baat karte rahe the, poore possible topics cover kar liye the us din, Fiitjee, Meerut, ex, KGP and blahhh. College life bhi humne usi tarah usi jagah baithkar end ki, usse better nai ho sakta tha last day apna. Bhale hi GALTI se tujhe itna door room de diya ho par vo kabhi bhi reason nai raha mere na aane ka. Tera room apne jaisa lagne laga tha. Kahi se bhi aati thi to pehle D731 mein aati thi. Sorry(nope) for 11:30pm things. You are the reason I donâ€™t hate lockdown. Kisi bhi time pe no time limit vaale calls, millie/coco ke videos, VCs and many other things you did for me. Jab tujhe Bye karke upar aayi thi tab tera room dekhke realize hua ki it will never be the same. Kaafi time tak tere room ke lock ko stare kar rahi thi, hall office vaala tha na ki jo maine lagaya tha second-year ki summers mein. Tab pata chala firse ki â€œitâ€™s not the place, but peopleâ€. And I got the best peopleðŸ–¤. Haan teri baat kar rahi hoon gawar. You know my deep deep deepest secrets jo mai kisi ko batane ka soch bhi nai sakti. You see through me like your white kurta(I love that btw).  Tu hadd special hai mere liye jitna tu soch bhi nai sakti. Poori Stats tune and tere notes ne padhai hai mujhe and seriously mere grades improvement ke credits bhi tujhe hi jaate hai. I survived on this campus because of you. 

Mai literally kaafi kuch aur likh sakti hoon tere baaare mein par kahin to rukna padhega. Bina mile US gayi to mai kabhi baat nai karungi. I find this word super lame but you are lamer, so here, â€œbestieâ€. Always be my 2 AM buddy. I love you so much that I can share my food with youðŸ–¤
